#While Alice was drinking sugarcane juice, she started wondering about the following facts:
The juicer sells each glass of sugarcane juice for 50 coins. He spends 20% of his total income on buying sugarcane.
He spends 20% of his total income on buying salt and mint leaves.
He spends 30% of his total income on shop rent. Alice wonders, what is the juicer's profit (in coins) when he sells N glasses of sugarcane juice?


t=int(input())
for i in range(t):
    N=int(input())
    a=50*N
    b=(0.2*a)+(0.2*a)+(0.3*a)
    print(int(a-b))
